name: isGirl
body:
This script can be used to check if a string (name) matches a girl name from a list of danish girl names.

### Authors and Contributors
Thanks to contributors: @klim8d and @pelleravn
tagline: Collection of code in different languages to check if a name is a girls name (danish girl names)
